    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although, at first when we came there, I think they wanted to be friendly, but it didn't work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What was a typical day like?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were very egalitarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to school, to classes together, but we also worked together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a very egalitarian thing of working together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In one sense, that has stayed with me, an egalitarian attitude about life.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
